data.title: Find ‘Meet the Press’ in your area
data.meta_description: Click here to find out on what station and at what time the program airs.
data.text:
**MEET THE PRESS VIEWERS PLEASE NOTE: This Sunday, June 8th, "Meet the Press" will air live at a special time of 8 am ET due to NBC's coverage of the French Open.**

The program also re-airs at 6 p.m. ET Sundays and 2 a.m. ET Mondays on MSNBC on cable. To check the time in your area, on NBC-TV or radio, check the list below.
